# ─── SMC Trading Bot — Local Runner Environment ───
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env.local to git.

# ─── Supabase (your existing project) ───
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...your-service-role-key...

# The runner calls your Edge Functions via HTTP, so they still run on Supabase.
# This is the HYBRID approach — local scheduler, cloud execution.
#
# For FULL LOCAL (no Supabase functions at all), you'd need to refactor
# each function into a direct import. See runner-direct.ts (future).
